 sites correpond to which crystal structure? (FCC vs HCP)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Identify the three-fold symmetry associated with the close-packed planes
 in many directions.
 In all, there are 4 such planes, perpendicular to the 4 different cube
 diagonals.
 The Miller indices are (111), ( ), ( ) and ( ).
