\begin_inset Formula $n\lambda=2dsin\theta$
\end_inset

, where n is an integer and diffraction (3-D sample) occurs at an angle
 
\begin_inset Formula $2\theta$
\end_inset

 from the incident direction.
 The spacing between atom planes is d.
 
\end_layout

